Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁 是谁在呼唤我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤我的是你对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你把我们的相遇当作秘密好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的你还在发什么梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 是个梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的大家都已经先走啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 把手抬起来啦！(做个万岁的动作）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元基 今天不用打工吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候不会有人去游戏机中心的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说这可是好几百年才能遇上的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 等下太阳月亮地球会在一条直线上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从地球上就看不到那边的太阳了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.78,0:05:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天这样太阳会完全被遮住的情况就叫做日全食
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！那个光芒四射的太阳会被月亮完全遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围就会变得一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是乎 是非常非常恐怖的日全食哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小孩说假话 你要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦小丽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始我就不会相信小兔的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我说错了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉！你该不会是刚刚不是在开玩笑 是认真的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么烦心事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈~那就是男孩子的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了命中注定的人之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哟 不能做让爸爸妈妈担心的事情哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是说你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:07:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近总是打工到很晚 妈妈很担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有光的夜晚竟然这么黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧?那个帐篷是什么东西 以前哪里有那东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔！你在干什么 我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发现！没发现！没发现！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小镇上的人都没有发现！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发现他们就是狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发现小孩子就是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小镇到处都是狗和猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然在小镇中间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了马戏团的帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.53,0:09:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙完全没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们根本不开心自己以外的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算老鼠把整个世界都啃光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算突然出现一个马戏团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个小镇也没有人会注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静！肃静！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在统治这个世界的时刻终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚马孙三重奏在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎眼在此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼眼在此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰眼在此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您找我们吗？吉鲁科尼亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 那家伙应该已经逃到这个世界的某处了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住那家伙 是我们征服这个世界的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.95,0:11:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务就交给你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 找出那些拥有美好梦想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好梦想…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是没办法在这个世界里长时间保持它的形态的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现实空间 他的力量会急速衰减然后死去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只有一个方法能让他在现世生存
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是隐匿于某人的美好的梦想之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么他已经隐匿到这个世界的某个人的美梦中了是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界非常大 人类也多如繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 拥有美好梦想的只有其中一小部分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能在其中找到那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去把它找出来！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说 这个女孩怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怎么样…她有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有美好梦想的人只是一小部分可还是有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好可爱~很难选啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你可别照着自己的喜好来选哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:12:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作第一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有她们哪里可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎眼 你喜欢这类的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼眼你的喜好也挺特别的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这女孩不错 就她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是照自己的喜好来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这种类型的女孩很难搞定哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这种女孩 只要装作是命运的相会就简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元基哥哥提到的那个男朋友啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在小孩面前讲些什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿~是在小孩子面前不能说的关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你！小兔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 这个挂坠里面就是那个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手！小小兔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还不算男朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然相处的气氛不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还没有明确的告白过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我们也许并不是命中注定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是女孩子也不能光坐着等白马王子出现啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候还得自己骑着白马去寻找王子才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是不是命运的相会 还是要看对方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想法好成熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 又擅自拿妈妈的成人小说来看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 钱包不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…是你的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太感谢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 能捡到这样的幸运宝物 我还赚到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.46,0:15:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜我们马上就要分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 你到底在搞什么啊 这么晚了还把我拖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有没有宽阔的森林里面有一个湖的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西小镇里不可能会有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…的确如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你受惊了我很抱歉 可爱的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 我不是什么可疑人物 请放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够可疑的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是宇奈月！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那奇怪的家伙是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是梦想之境了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里面会映出你的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:22.76,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}给我等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.05,0:16:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:26.68,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}爱与正义的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.06,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}水手服美少女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:34.88,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:37.01,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}和水手小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.35,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}我们要代替月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.21,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}惩罚你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…出现了两只奇怪的南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现吧 我的放射线妖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动人偶 断节公仔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是断节公仔~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心！出现了个怪东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断节公仔！替我干掉这两个南瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你要干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你能撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光璀璨的夜晚绝不允许低俗的恶魔来沾污…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕尾服假面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…你那是什么娘娘腔的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 我可不想被你说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乃是一只斩妖除魔的玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就来较量较量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵呵 中计了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那条鞭子已经把你的影子牢牢压在树干上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你就再也动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕尾服假面大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜~笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇奈月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让我来仔细窥探一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看那家伙有没有藏匿在你的美梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:18:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太遗憾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是个美丽的梦 不过那家伙不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很可怜 但是拥有美好梦想的人都得消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让那家伙无处藏身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断节公仔 把这些人全解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去大家都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁能借给我…力量啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他！是独角天马！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把两人都变成了超级水手月亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断节公仔！快把那两人都解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉有一股神秘的力量涌入体内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美丽啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！变回原来的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧只是失去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你 把我们的相遇当作秘密好吗……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 那不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的那个你是不是知道什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.66,0:21:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？没我什么也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.53,0:22:09.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,473)\fs29\fsp1}自从与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:14.50,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}心中的深处闪烁着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:20.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}无法舍弃对你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:25.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}只能静静的闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.01,0:22:29.76,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}过去的些许小事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:35.43,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}极为平常的言语也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:40.02,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}当想起之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:45.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}泪水就不知不觉的流出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:48.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(165,473)\fs29\fsp1}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:48.95,EDEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(247,483)\fs40\fsp1}Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:48.95,EDEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,480)\fs40\fsp1}Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:48.95,EDEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(449,480)\fs41\fsp1.5}love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:54.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}这样哭泣的夜晚也总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:23:00.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp1}怀念往昔 笑着相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:06.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,473)\fs29\fsp2}成为相爱的恋人吧......
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到命运般的相遇有多长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？ 你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是为了实现自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.78,0:23:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不得不和最喜欢的人分别的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般不会的啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想啊就是当小卫的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级再次变身 天马的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光传递着爱的讯息
